---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title='Listening — Bryan Yao'
  description='What Bryan is listening to — vinyl, shows, and the occasional stream.'
>
  <section class='column'>
    <h1 class='display title'>Listening</h1>
    <p class='smallcaps dek'>Vinyl first. The rest catches up.</p>

    <div class='body'>
      <p>
        <strong class='display'
          >Laufey — <em>Bewitched</em></strong
        ><br />
        2023, AWAL. Side A on most weekends. Kept as a vinyl ritual only —
        never streamed in the apartment, which keeps the needle doing real
        work and the record on the turntable until Monday.
      </p>
      <p>
        The apartment has one rule about music: if it's here, it plays on the
        record player. Streams are for commutes and gyms. Concerts and shows
        I go to get logged here after the fact.
      </p>
      <p class='smallcaps foot'>
        On deck: Billie Holiday, Norah Jones' <em>Come Away With Me</em>, a
        long-overdue first pressing of Kind of Blue.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .column {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 6rem;
  }
  .title {
    font-size: var(--step-5);
    color: var(--ivory-hi);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
  }
  .dek {
    color: var(--ivory-lo);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .body p {
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    color: var(--ivory);
  }
  .body em {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ivory-hi);
  }
  .body .foot {
    color: var(--ivory-lo);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    text-transform: none;
  }
  .body .foot em {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
</style>
